  Stable on SPARC.

  26 Nov 2004; Olivier Crete <tester@gentoo.org> tkabber-0.9.5b.ebuild:
  Remove sed in global scope

*tkabber-0.9.7 (26 Nov 2004)

  26 Nov 2004; Olivier Crete <tester@gentoo.org> -tkabber-0.9.3b-r1.ebuild,
  -tkabber-0.9.4b.ebuild, +tkabber-0.9.7.ebuild:
  Bumped to 0.9.7 (thanks to mikovits christian <gaelic@cargal.org>) 
  Fixed compilation with portage 2.0.51 (thanks to Alexander Kreuzer
  <a_kreuzer@gmx.de> and Rob Orlowsky <rob_is_not@hotmail.com>)
  Marked 0.9.6_beta stable on x86 and cleaned up old versions

  08 Aug 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> tkabber-0.9.6_beta.ebuild:
  Typo in DESCRIPTION: writen -> written. Bug 59717.

  19 Jun 2004; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> tkabber-0.9.6_beta.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc keyword.

  23 May 2004; Don Seiler <rizzo@gentoo.org>; tkabber-0.9.3b-r1.ebuild,
  tkabber-0.9.4b.ebuild, tkabber-0.9.5b.ebuild, tkabber-0.9.6_beta.ebuild:
  Updating package homepage

